    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>bread roll[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster </strong>for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Once toasted, top with the <strong>smashed avo </strong>and cut into triangles – this is your <strong>sumac smashed avo toast</strong></p>",
