    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>harissa shakshuka </strong>with the<strong> sumac smashed avo toast </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> remaining ground sumac </strong>over everything and season the egg[s] with a small pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
